# ✅ MVVM Architecture Refactor — Walkthrough

## What Was Done

The frontend codebase has been refactored to enforce strict MVVM layer separation while remaining fully backward-compatible. No pages were broken.

---

## MVVM Layer Map

| Layer | Where | Rule |
|---|---|---|
| **Model** | `modules/<domain>/{repository, service, types}` | Data fetching + transformation only. No Vue, no Pinia. |
| **ViewModel** | `stores/<domain>.store.ts` | State + actions. Uses services from Model layer only. |
| **View** | `pages/`, `components/`, `composables/use*.ts` | UI only. No direct [useApi()](file:///Users/paypanha/SMEFrontend/composables/useApi.ts#1-70) calls. |

---

